# Optimized Images Directory

This directory contains auto-generated optimized images in multiple formats and sizes.

**Do not edit files in this directory manually.**

Generated by the `npm run build:images` script from source images in `src/assets/images/`.

## Generated formats:
- AVIF (smallest, best quality)
- WebP (good compression, wide support)  
- JPEG (universal fallback)

## Generated sizes:
- 320px, 640px, 768px, 1024px, 1280px, 1440px, 1920px

## Files are automatically created:
- `{name}-{width}.avif`
- `{name}-{width}.webp` 
- `{name}-{width}.jpg`
- `{name}.json` (metadata)